Privacy Policy for Capture

Last updated: January 17, 2026

Capture (App) ("the App") is designed to help you capture ideas quickly.

DATA COLLECTION
- All your ideas are stored locally on your device only
- We do not collect, transmit, or store any personal data on external servers
- Voice input is processed on-device and is not sent to any server

DATA STORAGE
- Your ideas are stored using your device's local storage
- Data persists until you delete the app or clear app data

THIRD PARTIES
- We do not share any data with third parties
- We do not use analytics or tracking

CONTACT
For questions, contact: captureapplicationhelp@gmail.com
